Style connoisseur Zaynab Otiti Obanor is a woman with an uncommon aura and poise. Away from her ravishing beauty that could make a full-blooded man drool, the stylish woman is also blessed with the heart of gold. The philanthropist does not have limitations in meeting her set goals, more reason she is often described as a restless soul, who is constantly driven by an ambition to rule her world. 		 			Two years without Abba Kyari		 		 		 			Adekunle Olayinka is battle ready		 		 		 			Rotimi and Betty Akeredolu celebrate		 		 On Tuesday, April 19, 2022, the widely traveled Edo State-born added another year in a blaze of glory and devoid of the usual fanfare. She spent the greater part of the day in prayers to her creator for blessing her and making her see yet another year in good health and wealth. Many of her friends are always amazed at her humility and her total dependence on God in the most critical decisions of her life. ‘’Interestingly, many don’t understand that despite her successful career, she has not allowed fame, success, and stardom to turn her head. She recognizes that only God is the unseen hand behind her success story, and she submits absolutely to His will,” a source revealed.